Business Knowledge Base - WhatsApp AI Support System
Company Overview
Our company specializes in AI-powered automation, customer support chatbots, WhatsApp
automation, and cloud integration solutions. We help small and medium businesses streamline customer communication, reduce workload, and
improve response times using AI-driven workflows. Products & Services
1. AI-Powered WhatsApp Chatbot
• Automated replies for FAQs, orders, bookings, and support. • Context-aware conversation handling. • Integrated with internal business documents for accurate responses. 2. Customer Support Automation Platform
• Centralized dashboard for viewing customer interactions. • Chat analytics: message volume, response time, customer sentiment. • Multi-agent handover support. 3.

Basic Package
• Suitable for individuals and freelancers. • Handles up to 500 WhatsApp inquiries monthly. • Email support included. • Does not include analytics or customization. -- 1 of 3 --

Standard Package
• Ideal for small and medium businesses. • Up to 5,000 inquiries monthly. • Access to admin dashboard and analytics. • Limited customization options. • Priority email support. Premium Package
• Recommended for enterprises and high-volume users. • Unlimited inquiries. • Full customization + API access. • Dedicated account manager. • 24/7 priority support. • SLA-backed uptime guarantee.
